#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.logaddexp.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.logaddexp"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logaddexp.logaddexp:1 of
msgid "Logarithm of the sum of exponentiations of the inputs."
msgstr "输入指数和的对数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logaddexp.logaddexp:3 of
msgid ""
"Calculates ``log(exp(x1) + exp(x2))``. This function is useful in "
"statistics where the calculated probabilities of events may be so small "
"as to exceed the range of normal floating point numbers.  In such cases "
"the logarithm of the calculated probability is stored. This function "
"allows adding probabilities stored in such a fashion."
msgstr ""
"计算 ``log(exp(x1) + exp(x2))``。此函数在统计学中非常有用，因为事件的计算"
"概率可能非常小，以至于超出常规浮点数的范围。在这种情况下，会存储计算出的"
"概率的对数。此函数允许以这种方式存储的概率相加。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logaddexp.logaddexp of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logaddexp.logaddexp:9
#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logaddexp.logaddexp:11 of
msgid "Input values."
msgstr "输入值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logaddexp.logaddexp:13 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供了该参数，则其形状必须能够广播到输入的形状。"
"如果未提供或为 `None`，则返回一个新的 tensor。元组（只能作为关键字参数）"
"的长度必须等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logaddexp.logaddexp:18 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logaddexp.logaddexp:21 of
msgid ""
"For other keyword-only arguments, see the :ref:`ufunc docs "
"<ufuncs.kwargs>`."
msgstr "有关其他仅限关键字的参数，请参见 :ref:`ufunc 文档 <ufuncs.kwargs>`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logaddexp.logaddexp of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logaddexp.logaddexp:24 of
msgid "**result** -- Logarithm of ``exp(x1) + exp(x2)``."
msgstr "**result** -- ``exp(x1) + exp(x2)`` 的对数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logaddexp.logaddexp of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logaddexp.logaddexp:29 of
msgid ":py:obj:`logaddexp2`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logaddexp.logaddexp:30 of
msgid "Logarithm of the sum of exponentiations of inputs in base 2."
msgstr "以 2 为底的输入指数和的对数。"

